&lt;p&gt;Located near Checkpoint Charlie and set in a modernist, urban atmosphere, Tim Raue&rsquo;s cusine is Asian inspired with European technique, earning&nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;2016 World&rsquo;s 50 Best Restaurants #34,&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;#52&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;World&amp;#8217;s 50 Best Restaurants 2015 and Michelin 2 stars&lt;/strong&gt;. With the highest expectations of himself and his staff, service is polished but relaxed and dishes are delicious works of art. Business casual attire.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please book online at the Tim Raue website: &lt;a href=&quot;http://tim-raue.com/en/&quot;&gt;http://tim-raue.com/en/&lt;/a&gt; or contact Tim Raue by phone at +49 30 259 379 30 or email at email &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:office@tim-raue.com&quot;&gt;office@tim-raue.com&lt;/a&gt; to book your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell or local (hotel) phone number&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For up to 4 guests, no credit card is needed at the time of booking. For groups of 6 or more guests, Restaurant Tim Raue requires a credit card to hold your reservation. Your credit card will not be charged at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy- In case of a no show charges of 59,50 &euro; per person for lunch and 190,40 &euro; per person for dinner will be made to the credit card provided. Cancellations until 48 hours prior to the reservation are free of charge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: Please contact the restaurant by phone or email 48 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A main course must be purchased to receive your dining benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

